per at another New Zealand pharmacy? We'll beat the difference by 10%.\n                </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 DIVIDER \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;padding:0 30px;\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;font-size:0;height:1px;\">\n                      \u00a0\n                    </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 SOCIAL \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;padding:24px 30px 28px 30px;\">\n<p style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#222222;text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px 0;padding-bottom:0;\">\n                  Get social with us!\n                </p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:0 8px;\"> <a href=\"https://tiktok.com/@bargainchemistnz\" style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;\">\n<img alt=\"TikTok\" src=\"https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/assets/email/buttons/black/tiktok_96.png\" style=\"width:40px;height:40px;\" width=\"40\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding:0 8px;\"> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BargainChemist/\" style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;\">\n<img alt=\"Facebook\" src=\"https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/assets/email/buttons/black/facebook_96.png\" style=\"width:40px;height:40px;\" width=\"40\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding:0 8px;\"> <a href=\"https://instagram.com/bargainchemistnz\" style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;\">\n<img alt=\"Instagram\" src=\"https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/assets/email/buttons/black/instagram_96.png\" style=\"width:40px;height:40px;\" width=\"40\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding:0 8px;\"> <a href=\"https://nz.linkedin.com/company/bargain-chemist\" style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;\">\n<img alt=\"LinkedIn\" src=\"https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/company/XCgiqg/images/791081ec-bce5-4d35-9ee4-aa35ada53088.png\" style=\"width:40px;height:40px;\" width=\"40\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 LEGAL FOOTER \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#FF0031;padding:15px 30px 10px 30px;\">\n<p style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:9px;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;margin:0;padding-bottom:0;\">\n                  Please note that not all products may be available in all stores, please call your closest Bargain Chemist pharmacy or visit our\n                  <a href=\"https://www.bargainchemist.co.nz/pages/find-a-store\" style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;\">store locator</a>. Prices shown are online prices only and may differ to in store. Save price and Why Pay pricing is based on the recommended retailer price (RRP).\n                  <a href=\"https://www.bargainchemist.co.nz/pages/best-price-guarantee-our-policy-new-zealands-cheapest-chemist\" style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;\">Price beat guarantee</a> \u2014 If you find a cheaper everyday price on an identical in-stock item at a New Zealand pharmacy we will beat the difference by 10%. *Vitamins and minerals are supplementary to and not a replacement for a balanced diet. Always read the label, use only as directed. If symptoms persist, see your healthcare professional. Weight management products should be used with a balanced diet and exercise.\n                </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 UNSUBSCRIBE \u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#FF0031;padding:8px 18px 20px 18px;\">\n<p style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#ffffff;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;margin:0;padding-bottom:0;\">\n                  No longer want to receive these emails? {% unsubscribe 'Unsubscribe' %}.<br/>{{ organization.name }} {{ organization.full_address }}\n                </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- \u2500\u2500 UEMA & ASA Mandatory Footer (auto-injected) \u2500\u2500 -->\n<table bgcolor=\"#f4f4f4\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:16px 24px; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\n  font-size:11px; color:#888888; line-height:1.7;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\">\n<strong>Bargain Chemist Limited</strong>\u00a0\u00b7\u00a0\n    192 Moorhouse Avenue, Christchurch 8011, New Zealand\n  </p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0; font-size:10px; color:#aaaaaa;\">\n    Always read the label and use as directed.\n    If symptoms persist, see your healthcare professional.\n  </p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;\">\n<a href=\"{{ organization.homepage }}\" style=\"color:#FF0031; text-decoration:none;\">Visit our store</a>\n    \u00a0|\u00a0 {% unsubscribe 'Unsubscribe' %}\n  </p>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>","text":null,"amp":null,"created":"2026-05-06T09:50:50+00:00","updated":"2026-05-06T09:50:50+00:00"},"links":{"self":"https://a.klaviyo.com/api/templates/Tutaam/"}},"links":{"self":"https://a.klaviyo.com/api/templates/Tutaam/"}}